data.Bio: Homeboy Sandman grew up in Queens, New York City and attended boarding school at New Hampshireâ€™s Holderness School. He received an undergraduate degree from the University of Pennsylvania and subsequently enrolled in law school at Hofstra University. He withdrew from law school during his third year to pursue his career as an emcee. On June 1st 2010, Homeboy Sandman released his third album, The Good Sun.
